00:08:09.899 --> 00:08:12.579
for different reasons.

00:08:12.579 --> 00:08:22.339
When it gets to, you know, prediction, I'd say this is where you really want to make

00:08:22.339 --> 00:08:28.100
an intervention of some sort or, you know, you want to focus on a subset of your overall

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:36.659
