00:49:58.800 --> 00:50:07.760
Um, even when I started building Shiny apps, you know, basic Shiny is quite easy, but

00:50:10.560 --> 00:50:14.080
large functions underpin the entirety of a Shiny app.

00:50:14.080 --> 00:50:17.280
